data.description: Welcome home to Nazareth Borough! This wonderful home has 3 bedrooms and 1 bathroom. Eat in kitchen with a door that leads out to a covered large porch perfect for grilling and just relaxing. The lower level has many possibilities- there is a room that could be used as a den/office/playroom. Also,there is a large laundry room for folding and hanging your clothes, complete with a washer and dryer that will remain. There is an ample size room for storage or use as a walk in closet. Potential is there to make this a full bathroom. The rest of the lower level has space that can be turned into anything that fits your needs. There is a carport behind the house with plenty of parking. House backs up to a large alley. Refrigerator, and 4 A/C window units remain. Each room has their own temperature control. Transferable Home Warranty. Newer hot water heater. There are sidewalks to explore the Borough, lots of activities through out the year, a cute bakery just a few houses down and a park and soccer field across the street. Close to major highways, shopping, and restaurants.
